This is my second time getting filler and I’m so happy with how this one turned out! I wanted something that makes a difference to my lips but isn’t something that’s in your face or what they call ‘duck lips’. Dr. Zainab (I made a mistake in the video) hit the nail on the head with how she approached and filled my lips! I got 1ml of filler this time and the last time. The filler dissolves in about 6 months so it’s not permanent. So happy with them! If you have any questions leave them in the comments below!❤️ @skinlabindia @drjamunapai
